#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Old Mutations"
msgstr "舊版突變"

#. ~ Description for Old Mutations
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Makes mutations work like before, without balancing changes and mutagen "
"accumulation."
msgstr "使突變像以前一樣運作，沒有平衡性調整和誘變劑積累。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Robust Genetics"
msgstr "強健基因"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Robust Genetics'}
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"You have a very strong genetic base.  If you mutate, the odds that the "
"mutation will be beneficial are greatly increased."
msgstr "你擁有非常強大的基因基礎。如果發生突變，有益突變的幾率會大大增加。"
